.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-POLICY-CHECK" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-policy-check \- flag unusual fee policies on channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-policy-check
.SH DESCRIPTION
Inspects the local fee policy on each
.B CHANNELD_NORMAL
channel and returns channels with unusual settings.
Flags include
.BR high_ppm ,
.BR high_base_fee ,
.BR high_htlc_min ,
and
.BR low_htlc_max .
Returns an empty array if no issues are found or the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, flags:[...]}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-fee-policy (1),
.BR lightning-channel-set-fee (1)
